{"tid":2227941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普已使用瑞德西韋，再貼文稱情況良好","createTime":"2020-10-03T07:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T07:38:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d7181bb1ac6f25ae58c1a167f2342974d9cf077f","tid":2227941,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552869-20201003.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552869-20201003.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmeaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=ca42a4b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1552869-20201003.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d73e04e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1552869-20201003.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n確診感染武漢肺炎的美國總統特朗普按醫生的建議，正在軍方醫療中心接受治療，白宮稱這是預防措施。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在社交網站上載片段，他說自己情況良好，但他看起來有些疲態，聲線較低沉。他之後再發文，表示相信情況有好轉，感謝各人支持。<br />\n<br />\n白宮醫生表示，特朗普情況良好，不需聞氧氣，已使用抗病毒藥物「瑞德西韋」，較早前他亦使用多種藥物的雞尾酒療法。<br />\n<br />\n有傳媒引述消息人士指出，特朗普有輕微發燒、咳嗽及鼻塞。"},{"pid":"061bb9762129f3a4fab0b813f0f1a4713e1668b0","tid":2227941,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}